The paper focuses on object detection using deep CNN models, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of ensemble models and data augmentation also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The inclusion of the Microsoft COCO dataset and the use of evaluation metrics suggest a focus on multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
